{"tid":1844324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈：我哋已經放棄咗政府，唔係政府放棄我哋！","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:01:28.000Z","uid":157103,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d73e2008e5eefaf2645a2129f7a774801bed852d","tid":1844324,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎已經殺到香港，政府到依家仲未封關，證明咗中共準備滅絕我哋香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由回歸以嚟，港共政府一直逼害我哋香港人，仲有咩資格管理香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n權力一直來自人民，既然政府已無能管理香港，我哋就自己掌握返自己命運。<br />\n<br />\n有個問題R爆頭都諗唔明，點解係我哋求依個無能政府？既然政府一直無視五大訴求，我哋就攞返主導權！<br />\n<br />\n1月29 大三罷 事在必行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a336156af4df73573c1b46d2356d279adbdc55","tid":1844324,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"全民參政<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1844124/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1844124/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3637faf22143b72b71bf23126f42cde71a36e815","tid":1844324,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面封關</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8a856711c82773d7ac92dbcf208706ad649045c","tid":1844324,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"民主從來都唔係指市民盲目相信政府<br />\n<br />\n民主指嘅係市民有渠道可以監察政府<br />\n唔俾佢行錯方向<br />\n所以民主嘅社會 市民唔信政府係正常<br />\n因為政府可能會有朝一日出賣市民<br />\n出賣自己應該要保護嘅對象<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>正如今時今日嘅香港政府一樣</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋冇得揀特首 冇得揀政府<br />\n但係我哋有得揀一條保護自己嘅路黎行"},{"pid":"0650e768e2feb18f07c89d615e8143392d8c1320","tid":1844324,"uid":100273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"一早已經要，呢個政府早就失去左管治權"},{"pid":"76160c9bd3de0ae7a6f5c0134b0b4ebc562ccf77","tid":1844324,"uid":281096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"立即封關 香港獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845884</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}